Mami is home. Dom comes out to explain himself but they’re interrupted by Liv Morgan on screen.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/6d09a1fa-74ed-4fa9-ae3f-cfb083165c1c/20240715_171231.jpg?format=original)

## **_“Sorry about the voice... I had a long weekend in Mexico and I’ve always been known to be quite the screamer”_**

## **_\- Liv Morgan to Rhea Ripley_**

Liv vs Rhea is officially on for Summerslam

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/d34fc699-04b2-455d-9fdc-ef5e6d3fd8fb/20240715_173648.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_SHEAMUS DEF. BRONSON REED AND GETS ATTACKED BY PETE DUNNE_**
    

Sheamus also had TOO MANY LIMES taken away from him 💔💔💔

A bad day for Sheamus and his fans

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/c70dc02a-9ac0-4cb0-bb34-435f4568c4aa/20240715_175446.jpg?format=original)

Zelina Vega roasted Sonya Deville backstage leading to a quick match that ended when Sonya's crew jumped Zelina.

Kayden Carter, Katana Chance and Lyra Valkyria run out to save Zelina from further harm

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/39c12760-605c-42c3-9a79-20cfb1baf4b8/Screenshot_20240715_175525.jpg?format=original)

Jey Uso trying to get a piece of Rhea Ripley for himself.

“If you see Mami. Tell her I said YEET.”

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/040ccfb3-bd77-402f-a699-d82862c01edb/20240715_180829.jpg?format=original)

A video played with GUNTHER reminding everyone that while he always wanted to be a wrestler, his dream was never to be a WWE Superstar. He joined WWE to save it from garbage.

Damian Priest and Gunther come out for the face off. Priest tells Gunther that if WWE wasn't his dream then WWE doesn't need privileged people like him. He tells Gunther that while he was being handed everything in Europe, Priest was on the streets fighting for his life.

Gunther says he wasn't handed anything, he's just that talented. And while STREET TRASH like Damien Priest was "fighting for his life"

WWE was begging GUNTHER to come over and save then from garbage like Damien Priest calling himself World Champion.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f90633f9-6380-4a30-b63c-e7e651a44475/20240715_182535.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_DAMIEN PRIEST DEF. BRAUN STROWMAN_**
    

After the match, GUNTHER comes out and just chops Priest in the chest. They brawl until Priest clears the ring and stands alone.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/a233f8ee-6333-41c5-aedd-6fc3bfc907eb/20240715_182810.jpg?format=original)

Chad Gable overhears Otis, Tozawa and Maxine talking about helping out their friend. He’s happy they’re going to help him call out Bo Dallas tonight.

But they weren’t talking about him. They were talking about helping Xavier Woods take on the Final Testament.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/b4efe67b-006e-4ed3-a569-3cfd9be1ea28/20240715_185211.jpg?format=original)

Dominik tells Rhea he got a match against Jey Uso tonight because Uso was disrespectful. Rhea asks what was Dom thinking picking a fight with Jey?

Dom says he'll cancel it. Rhea says wait, what is he? A coward?

Dom says he just wants to show Jey Uso that Rhea is his Mami and she BELONGS to him 😬😬😬😬

Rhea storms off. Carlito says....

Not cool.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/416ad900-de7a-452e-921c-34988c504575/20240715_190001.jpg?format=original)

Adam Pearce brings Drew McIntyre out to the ring and asks him how much does he want this match with CM Punk?

Drew says more than anything in the world. Pearce says Drew can have the match if he apologizes to the refs he hurt at Clash at the Castle.

Drew refuses. Adam Pearce says Drew still suspended. Drew starts attacking the refs again until Seth Rollings runs out for the save.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/9370f433-882e-4334-ae75-c6e43fb16cec/20240715_190227.jpg?format=original)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/2f460098-1ce2-4e55-b56b-b6c7003bb4af/Screenshot_20240715_190833.jpg?format=original)

Absolutely powerful promo from Erick Rowan talking about the loss of his Wyatt Family brothers and Bo Dallas reaching out to him.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/d8fa1efb-4314-4b54-bcc9-1fbe06f61ad0/20240715_193046.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_JEY USO DEF. DOMINIK MYSTERIO_**
    

Liv Morgan distracts Dom and she grapples her way onto his crotch again. Rhea is there and she looks disappointed in Dom...

She finds Dom backstage and sets things straight. She doesn't belong to ANYONE... But Dom belongs to her. 🖤🖤

HES BACK IN THE GAME!!!!!!!!!!!!

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/c0d2a693-2907-44fb-875e-3f887718ccfd/20240715_193436.jpg?format=original)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/8e90cb12-4e2b-441f-bb9d-800bdd558ff5/20240715_193721.jpg?format=original)

Chad Gable calls out Bo Dallas but the Creed Bros jump Bo from behind.

They beat down Bo Dallas but Dallas just laughs the entire time.

"YEAH YEAH YEAH YEAH YEAH (Brodie Lee-esque)

THERE YOU ARE..... YEAH YEAH YEAH YEAH YEAH.."

LIGHTS OUT. THE WYATT 6 ARE HERE.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/d0ec6104-0b56-4682-bf71-bbe1451546a1/20240715_194005.jpg?format=original)

