![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/2ae0dc78-c590-4ff3-8569-9e7d28b455fa/20240715_200146.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_SAMI ZAYN VS ILJA DRAGUNOV ENDS IN A NO CONTEST_**
    

Bron Breakker runs around the ring. He spears Dragunov and beats on Sami Zayn.

WWE RAW ends with Bron Breamker standing tall over Sami Zayn

